This hardly seems like a recipe, but every time I serve it, people ask me how to make it. So here it is! This is great with a green salad or a composed salad. Variations: Lemon Vinaigrette: Substitute lemon juice for the lime juice in lime vinaigrette. Cumin Vinaigrette: Add Â½ teaspoon ground cumin to lemon Vinaigrette. In a small bowl, whisk together the lemon juice and salt. Drizzle the olive oil in a fine stream into the bowl while whisking to combine.